<div class="ui inverted attached segment" id="footer">
    <div class="ui center aligned wide container">
        <div class="ui stackable inverted divided grid">
            <div class="seven wide column">
                <h4 class="ui inverted header">What is Totally Not Another PHP Framework?</h4>
                <p>
                    Totally Not Another PHP Framework (TNAPF) is a lightweight PHP framework designed to make web
                    development easier and more efficient. TNAPF's acronym is a nod to the common complaint that there
                    are already too many PHP frameworks out there. You can use as much of TNAPF as you want in pair with
                    tools you've already come to love. Whether you are a seasoned developer or just
                    starting out, TNAPF can help you build web applications quickly and efficiently.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="three wide column">
                <h4 class="ui inverted header">Resources</h4>
                <div class="ui inverted link list">
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/tnapf" class="item">Github</a>
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://discord.gg/TgrcSkuDtQ" class="item">Discord</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three wide column">
                <h4 class="ui inverted header">Packages</h4>
                <div class="ui inverted link list">
                    {% for repo in github().repositories %}
                        <a target="_blank" href="{{ repo.html_url }}" class="item">{{ repo.name }}</a>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="developers three wide column">
                <h4 class="ui inverted header">Members</h4>
                <div class="ui inverted link list">
                    {% for member in github().members %}
                    <a target="_blank" class="item" href="{{ member.html_url }}">
                        <img src="{{ member.avatar_url }}" alt="{{ member.login }}'s profile picture" class="ui avatar image">
                        <span>{{ member.login }}</span>
                    </a>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ui inverted section divider"></div>
        <img src="/img/logo.png" class="ui centered tiny image">
        <div class="ui horizontal inverted small divided link list">
            <a href="https://githhub.com/tnapf/privacy" class="item">Privacy Police</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/tnapf/cookies" class="item">Cookie Policy</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
